text: Javier Gómez Fuertes (born 5 December 1986) is a Spanish gymnast. He competed in seven events at the 2012 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1986 births Category:Living people Category:Spanish male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Spain Category:Gymnasts at the 2012 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts from Barcelona
